1. *Mirno* je plivala u moru. (She was swimming peacefully in the sea.)
2. *Mirno* je sjedila u parku. (She was sitting peacefully in the park.)
3. *Mirno* je prespavala cijelu noć. (She slept peacefully all night.)
4. *Mirnoć* glavnog grada je bila nevjerovatna. (The peace of the capital city was incredible.)
5. *Mirno* je krenula prema kući. (She walked peacefully towards home.)
6. *Mirnoću* je prekrio čitav grad. (Peace covered the entire city.)